description: Gets the list of Images in the subscription. Use nextLink property in the response to get the next page of Images. Do this till nextLink is null to fetch all the Images.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

nextlink.description: The uri to fetch the next page of Images. Call ListNext() with this to fetch the next page of Images.
